title: Assassin's Creed Meets Parkour in Real Life
description: Watch the Behind The Scenes in this link below: http://youtu.be/36CLFOyaml0 Make sure to subscribe to this channel for new vids each week! http://youtube.com/devinsupertramp Parkour/Free Running stunts performed by Ronnie Shalvis. Make sure to check out his youtube channel and facebook page! http://youtube.com/ronniestreetstunts https://www.facebook.com/ronniestreet...
